win in seven starts and Darren Bragg singled in the winning run in the seventh
inning as the Colorado Rockies beat the San Diego Padres 5-4 Friday night. It
was Astacio's 23rd career complete game and his third this season, but first in
a winning effort. He allowed four runs on six hits, struck out 11 and walked one
in the Rockies' third straight win.
</P>
